# Crab Rollup


## Ingredients
This salsa is tasty and easy to make. Just a little bit of peppers adds enough
hot, but add more for more spice to your life.

- 3 to 4 roma tomatoes (finely diced)
- ยน/2 red onion, diced
- 1 serrano chilli pepper (stems, ribs, seedremoved) diced.
- Juice of one lime
- 1/4 cup chopped cilantro
- 1/4 cup chopped black olives
- Sea salt

## Instructions

1. Mix all ingredients together, season with salt and chill for an hour.

